data.description: Welcome to this beautiful modern farmhouse style home that is perfectly located on a large corner lot at the edge of town. This one of a kind property provides it all: the convenience of being in town combined with the highly sought after experience of rural living. You will appreciate the tranquility of uninterrupted and expansive views of the picturesque mountain ranges and Kremmling cliffs. Whether you are an outdoor enthusiast looking for a central location to begin your many adventures or looking for a peaceful place to call home, this property will maximize your enjoyment & lifestyle. Come sip some coffee and enjoy the serene views on the wrap-around covered porch or meander the path to visit your chickens in their large coop. A distinct feature of this property is that every aspect of the outdoor living space has been expertly designed to enhance your experience and enjoyment. Featuring high-end professional landscaping throughout, Wi-Fi enabled outdoor lighting and irrigation system. As you enter this home you will be greeted by the bright and open modern farmhouse style complete with tons of windows, custom woodworking, shiplap accents, modern hardware, beautiful lighting and pleasing color palette. The main level features a lovely living room with windows everywhere and a wood stove for those cozy nights. Continue in to find a large office with separate entrance, chef's kitchen, a dining room with wrap-around windows that is perfect for entertaining. Down the hall is a full bath, fun bonus loft area and beautiful master suite. On the lower level you will find a large living room, three bedrooms, full bath, and laundry room. This home highlights quality of build that includes radiant floor heat throughout that creates ease of mountain living even in the coldest months of the year. And a large detached HEATED shop for anyone who has toys and/or year round hobbies.  A remarkable property like this does not come along very often - do not miss your opportunity!
